description:
This is a 11 minute workout called 'Lower Body Strength with Bands' from the channel Peter Donohoe.
The workout falls under Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Other for this workout.
The workout has a The Masterclass Workout and The Rhythmic Powerhouse vibe.
The The Masterclass Workout vibe means Technique-driven, focused, skill-building. This is especially good for Those who love precision and mastery in movement. The The Rhythmic Powerhouse vibe means Beat-driven, strong but fluid, music-infused. This is especially good for When you want strength and rhythm to blend seamlessly..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Build strength in your lower body with Pete during short exercises that incorporate your resistance band....
